data.description:
UPDATE: LOCATED: Hannah K Guerrier has been safely recovered. She is in good health. 

Initial post
Port St Lucie Police seek public's help locating missing endangered fourteen-year-old Hannah K Guerrier.  

Hannah Guerrier was last seen on June 8, at around 6:00 pm when she left her home located in Port St. Lucie.  She was last seen wearing a long sleeve black shirt, ripped blue jeans and multi-colored checkered van sneakers.  

Hannah Guerrier is a black female, 5'07" tall, 125 lbs, black hair and brown eyes.  

If anyone has information about her whereabouts, please contact: Detective K. Meyer Office # (772) 807-4400. You can be anonymous, call Treasure Coast Crime Stoppers 800-273-TIPS (8477)
